Sitting in their living room with a school photo of Peter - also known by the Islamic name Abdul-Rahman in the background, Mr Kassig told CBS: 'The dynamics have changed now. Steven's [Sotloff] family kept to secrecy, and he was executed. Peter's name has been listed.'

In the audio recording Peter said his life was in jeopardy if U.S. airstrikes did not stop.

'It was just automatic, kind of toneless, as though he was a robot,' Mrs Kassig said.

Peter with his mother as a child. He is the Kassig's only child. The couple said they hope their son will learn of their TV appearance - either directly or indirectly - and 'know we are doing everything we can to secure his release'

